item.description:
@tonypker13 wrote:

[quote=“xstrxpurez, post:2, topic:237412”][quote author=tonypker13 link=topic=313463.msg2495284#msg2495284 date=1224367009]
okay, so I made the wildy ditch work once by making it open an interface, then i had to delete the source.
Does anyone know the code to open up an interface?
I was thinking something like this.

case ####;
{
							p.frames.showInterface(p, InterfaceID);
						}

And if that’s right,
Does any1 know the wildy ditch interface ID?
[/quote]

go to ur list folder and the interfaces are in there… and u need the case id on the ditch.
heres the interface to show it…

		p.frames.showInterface(p, ###);

Ahhh so I was correct. Thanks.
